            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1949-01-05T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1947-05-04T17:00:00-05:00" n="156" subtype="editorial-note" type="document" xml:id="d156">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>The Economic Cooperation Administration, through December 31, 1948, made
                    procurement authorizations of commodities and services totaling $145,700,000 for
                    Greece and $1,700,000 for Turkey. (<hi rend="italic">Third Report to Congress of
                        the Economic Cooperation Administration</hi>, Washington, Government
                    Printing Office, 1949, page 134.)</p>
            </div>
        </body>
